=== SUBSCRIPT with post-increment index ===
subscript_assign: i=1 (expect 1)
subscript_compound: i=1 arr[0]=15 (expect i=1 arr[0]=15)
subscript_predec: i=2 arr[2]=99 (expect i=2 arr[2]=99)

=== DEREF with side-effecting operand ===
deref_assign: calls=1 (expect 1)
deref_compound: calls=1 arr[0]=11 (expect calls=1 arr[0]=11)

=== ARROW with side-effecting base ===
arrow_assign: calls=1 s.x=42 (expect calls=1 s.x=42)
arrow_compound: calls=1 s.x=15 (expect calls=1 s.x=15)

=== INCREMENT/DECREMENT on complex lvalue ===
preinc_deref: calls=1 arr[0]=11 (expect calls=1 arr[0]=11)
postinc_deref: calls=1 arr[0]=11 (expect calls=1 arr[0]=11)
preinc_arrow: calls=1 s.x=11 (expect calls=1 s.x=11)
